                                            Want to earn commissions? <a href="/promoter/register" class="mil-accent">Become a Promoter (Free)</a>
                                        </p>
                                        <p class="mil-text-s mil-soft">
                                            Want premium benefits? <a href="/business-partner/register" class="mil-accent">Become a Business Partner</a>
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        </div>
