                                    <p class="mil-text-m mil-soft mil-mb-30">"The developers I connected with through RevaampAPA transformed my land into a profitable real estate project. The cheap development funds made it possible!"</p>
                                    <img src="/img/faces/1.jpg" alt="Customer" style="width: 80px; height: 80px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; margin-bottom: 15px;">
