                            <div class="mil-accordion">
                                <div class="mil-accordion-group mil-up">
                                    <div class="mil-accordion-menu">
                                        <h5>How much does it cost to list a property?</h5>
                                        <div class="mil-accordion-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mil-accordion-content">
                                        <p class="mil-text-m mil-soft">Property owners pay a one-time verification fee of ₦20,000 per property. There are no monthly fees or hidden charges. You can list unlimited properties after verification.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mil-accordion-group mil-up">
                                    <div class="mil-accordion-menu">
                                        <h5>How do I unlock capital from my property before sale?</h5>
                                        <div class="mil-accordion-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i></div>
